  "contentHtml": "<h1>break</h1>\n<p>You can use the break keyword to jump out of loops.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-php\"><span class=\"hljs-meta\">&#x3C;?php</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$i</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0</span>; <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$i</span> &#x3C; <span class=\"hljs-number\">10</span>; <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$i</span>++) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">echo</span> <span class=\"hljs-variable\">$i</span>;\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-variable\">$i</span> == <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>) <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">break</span>;\n}\n<span class=\"hljs-meta\">?></span>\n</code></pre>",
